@startuml
title sd Диаграмма последовательности

skinparam backgroundColor #ECECEC
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #E3E3E3
  BorderColor #666666
  FontColor #111111
}
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #ECECEC
  BorderColor #666666
  FontColor #111111
}
skinparam sequence {
  LifeLineBorderColor #8A8A8A
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F2F2F2
  ParticipantBorderColor #666666
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #E3E3E3
  ArrowColor #222222
  ActorBorderColor #666666
}

actor "Фронтенд\n(создатель)" as Creator
actor "Фронтенд\n(модератор)" as Moderator
participant ": Домен\nUsers" as Users
participant ": Домен\nServices" as Services
participant ": Домен\nClaims" as Claims
participant ": Домен\nM-M" as MM
participant "Расчет XRF\n(внутри FormClaim)" as Calc

Creator -> Users: 1 : POST /api/users/auth\n(login,password)
Users --> Creator: 2 : JSON JWT + role + session_id + expires_at

Creator -> Services: 3 : GET /api/services?q=bronze
Services --> Creator: 4 : JSON список услуг

Creator -> Claims: 5 : GET /api/claims/cart-icon
Claims --> Creator: 6 : JSON корзина (id черновика, количество)

Creator -> MM: 7 : POST /api/claim-items\n(service_id:1)
MM --> Creator: 8 : JSON услуга добавлена в черновик

Creator -> MM: 9 : POST /api/claim-items\n(service_id:2)
MM --> Creator: 10 : JSON добавлена 2-я услуга

Creator -> Claims: 11 : GET /api/claims/{claim_id}
Claims --> Creator: 12 : JSON черновик заявки + 2 услуги

Creator -> MM: 13 : PUT /api/claim-items/{service_id_1}\n(quantity,sort_order)
MM --> Creator: 14 : JSON m-m обновлена

Creator -> Claims: 15 : PUT /api/claims/{claim_id}\n(operator_comment,cu,zn,sn,pb)
Claims --> Creator: 16 : JSON черновик обновлен

Creator -> Claims: 17 : PUT /api/claims/{claim_id}/moderate\n(action:"complete")
Claims --> Creator: 18 : 403 JSON недостаточно прав

Creator -> Claims: 19 : PUT /api/claims/{claim_id}/form
Claims -> Calc: 20 : Расчет формулы состава и score
Calc --> Claims: 21 : result_value[] + best_match + total_cost
Claims --> Creator: 22 : 200 JSON заявка сформирована

Moderator -> Users: 23 : POST /api/users/auth\n(login,password)
Users --> Moderator: 24 : 200 JSON JWT (роль moderator)

Moderator -> Claims: 25 : PUT /api/claims/{claim_id}/moderate\n(action:"complete")
Claims --> Moderator: 26 : 200 JSON status=completed

Moderator -> Claims: 27 : GET /api/claims
Claims --> Moderator: 28 : 200 JSON список всех заявок

@enduml
